		<title>The Hacks for Hacks Guide to Writing Awards</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WriterUnboxed/~3/Exzoef8sBfA/</link>
		<comments>http://writerunboxed.com/2015/01/17/the-hacks-for-hacks-guide-to-writing-awards/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 17 Jan 2015 12:00:01 +0000</pubDate>
